# 📊 Power Query Data Cleaning Project

## 📌 Overview
This project demonstrates data cleaning and transformation using Power Query in Excel. It includes operations like cleaning data, splitting and merging columns, removing duplicates, and applying conditional formatting in Excel.

---

## 🧹 1. Data Cleaning
- Removed null values
- Fixed spelling errors (e.g., Electroni → Electronics)
- Standardized text format
- Changed data types (Text, Number, Date)

---

## 🔀 2. Splitting and Merging Columns

### Splitting
- Full Name → First Name + Last Name
- Product Code → Separate components

### Merging
- First Name + Last Name → Full Name
- Product attributes combined into single column

---

## 🔁 3. Removing Duplicates
- Identified duplicate rows using key columns
- Removed repeated records using Power Query "Remove Duplicates"
- Ensured clean and unique dataset

---

## 🎨 4. Conditional Formatting (Excel)

After loading data from Power Query:
- Applied **Data Bars** to Price column
- Used **Color Scales** to show price variations
- Highlighted "Electronics" category using custom rules

---

